        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p><strong>A,B,V TestMaker</strong> (“the App”) respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains what information the App collects, how it is used, and your rights.</p>
        
        <h2>1. Information Collection</h2>
        <p>The App <strong>does not collect, store, or share any personal information</strong> from users. It works entirely offline and reads only the contents of TXT files provided by the user.</p>
        
        <h2>2. Usage of Data</h2>
        <p>The App processes the content of TXT files locally to generate interactive tests. <strong>No data is sent to any servers or third parties.</strong></p>
        
        <h2>3. Permissions</h2>
        <p>The App <strong>does not request any permissions</strong> from the user’s device except the ability to read TXT files selected by the user.</p>
        
        <h2>4. Advertising</h2>
        <p>The App uses <strong>AdMob advertising</strong> to support its development. AdMob may collect anonymized usage data according to its own Privacy Policy: 
            <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">AdMob Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>
        
        <h2>5. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>The App may integrate third-party services (like AdMob) for advertisements. These services have their own privacy policies, which are independent of A,B,V TestMaker.</p>
        
        <h2>6. Data Security</h2>
        <p>Since the App does not store or transmit any personal information, no personal data security risks are present.</p>
        
        <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, you can contact us at: 
            <a href="mailto:asadbekalfa808@gmail.com">asadbekalfa808@gmail.com</a>
        </p>
    </div>
